author: Ronn Blitzer
title: Michigan Gov. Whitmer facing backlash for going to 'radical extremes' with stay-at-home order
description: Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer is facing backlash following an expansion to her state's stay-at-home order that prohibits not just public gatherings, but private ones as well -- regardless of size or family ties -- in response to the coronavirus pandemic.
